<collectingRegion box="[1584,1717,1273,1298]" country="United Kingdom" name="Highland" pageId="180" pageNumber="942">Highland</collectingRegion>
forests, including wet montane forests, at elevations of 
<quantity box="[2485,2667,1273,1298]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.475" metricValueMax="3.45" metricValueMin="1.5" pageId="180" pageNumber="942" unit="m" value="2475.0" valueMax="3450.0" valueMin="1500.0">1500-3450 m</quantity>
(rarely below 
<quantity box="[1659,1765,1303,1336]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.0" pageId="180" pageNumber="942" unit="m" value="1000.0">1000 m</quantity>
