<paragraph blockId="180.[1461,2669,720,1692]" pageId="180" pageNumber="942">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1463,1812,1541,1574]" pageId="180" pageNumber="942">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. The Montane 
<taxonomicName box="[1533,1623,1580,1613]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="180" pageNumber="942" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Myotis</taxonomicName>
